,Recommended,407230,25801595,"Posted: 1 October, 2016",all,nerrnerr,"Legend of Mysteria is a really nice game with rich story and detailed concepts. It's not your everyday JRPG with many hours of grinding and leveling up, since there is no such thing as a leveling up system in this game. You need to search high and low in order to find clues that help you prove your innocence regarding a murder case.The story, the soundtracts selected, the characters' personalities are all amazing, BUT it is required of you to find all the clues in order to prove your innocence which is quite time consuming(considering that one less interaction with an object can lead to you getting the bad ending)and without the help of a guide really frustrating at times.Despite that, I would like to recommend this game to everyone and anyone, who is willing to learn about a new colorful world with detailed characters and plot that will keep you invested in the story of Windir~P.S. Fangirled so hard at the Windir+Triste moments!"
